title: Bella Natural Food
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Australian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Family-owned cafe, deli, fruit and vegetable store. Sells organic natural foods, local foods, preserves, marinades, house-made dips, and gluten free products. Serves Toby's Estate coffee beans. Stocks soy and rice milks for coffee. Deli offers a selection of prepared salads, wraps and rolls, pastries, fruit salad, and house-made sweets. Fresh juices and smoothies start from 7am, using only organic carrots as well as other seasonal organic ingredients.
